item.title: How to change Starter point and teleports!? plz help (317 DELTA)
item.dc:creator: @Mellor Mellor
item.description:
@Mellor wrote:

If you go onto your player file. Then ctr+f , type in “initial x” , this will bring you to something like this.

// initial x and y coordinates of the player heightLevel = 0; // the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper // initialization packet toX = 3088; toY = 3502;

Yep, to change your initial spawn point, you will want to change the

toX = 3088; toY = 3502;

To your coords.

If you wanted to add the spawn point upstairs anywhere, or underground.You change the

		heightLevel = 0;

Goodluck =p
